text: André Luis Gaspar Janones (born 5 May 1984) is a Brazilian lawyer and politician. He is a member of Avante. He has been a federal deputy for Minas Gerais since 2019. He ran for President of Brazil in the 2022 election. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1984 births Category:Brazilian lawyers Category:Politicians from Minas Gerais
